dataset.title: The Oldest Tenebrionidae (Coleoptera) Of The Subfamily Diaperinae And The Tribe Scaphidemini From The Paleocene Of Menat (France)

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Nabozhenko, Maxim V., Kirejtshuk, Alexander G. (2020): The Oldest Tenebrionidae (Coleoptera) Of The Subfamily Diaperinae And The Tribe Scaphidemini From The Paleocene Of Menat (France). Acta Zoologica Academiae Scientiarum Hungaricae 66 (1): 23-33, DOI: 10.17109/AZH.66.1.23.2020, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.17109/azh.66.1.23.2020
